  "body": "This issue refers to the `Create a backup copy of a Keycard` flow, which starts here:\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/idUoxN7OIW2Jpp3PMJ1Rl8/%E2%9A%99%EF%B8%8F-Settings-%7C-Desktop?node-id=7258%3A188522\r\n\r\nPart of Keycard settings part which is the epic tracked under https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/issues/4920\r\n\r\nCriteria covered by this issue:\r\n\r\n### Stage 1. \r\n\r\nSelect option to backup\r\n\r\n**- Attaching keycard**\r\n\r\n1. If reader is not attached show Plug in card reader. \r\n2. If reader is attached and card is not inserted show insert keycard\r\n3. If reader is removedâ€¦ \r\n\r\n**- Invalid keycard**\r\n\r\n1. If inserted card is not a keycard show - This is not a keycard modal\r\n2. If inserted card is not linked to account - Wrong keycard inserted\r\n3. If inserted card is empty - Keycard is empty\r\n4. If inserted card is locked - Keycard locked\r\n\r\n**- Keycard recognised**\r\n \r\n1. Enter PIN\r\n2. Invalid PIN - Factory reset\r\n3. Invalid PIN - Locked after 3 attempts\r\n\r\n- Accounts on this keycard\r\n- Extended accounts on this keycard\r\n\r\n### Stage 2.\r\n\r\n- Remove card\r\n- Insert empty keycard\r\n- Reading keycard\r\n\r\n1. Is it a keycard\r\n2. Is it a different card\r\n3. Is card locked\r\n\r\n**Route A**\r\n1. Is keycard empty.\r\n2. Copy keycard to insterted card\r\n3. Enter seed phrase\r\n4. Valid seed phase\r\n5. Copying keycard\r\n6. Keycard is now a copy.\r\n\r\n**Route B**\r\n####  - keycard not empty\r\n1. enter pin - > factory reset\r\n2. wrong pin -> locked after 3 tries\r\n3. Pin verified\r\n\r\n#### - keycard known by profile\r\n1. accounts on this card\r\n2. Factory reset are you sure\r\n3. Yes sure\r\n4. Factory resetting\r\n5. keycard has been reset.\r\n\r\n#### -  keycard not known\r\n1. accounts on card\r\n2. I understand\r\n3. Factory resetting\r\n4. keycard reset",
